\newlabel{tab:mini_benchmark_species}{{7}{22}{Mini-benchmark species and their associated datasets. Pantera consensi are sequences identified by the Pantera pipeline in each species' genome. The curated library is an externally curated RepeatMasker-format TE reference library used as the primary evaluation set. Structural LTR sequences are confirmed LTR-class elements detected by genome-wide LTR-terminal-repeat alignment, carrying genomic coordinate metadata but no superfamily annotation}{table.caption.17}{}}
